sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Chain
    participant Memory
    participant LLM

    User->>Chain: New message
    Chain->>Memory: 1. load_memory_variables()
    Memory->>Chain: Returns context
    Chain->>LLM: 2. Prompt = context + new message
    LLM->>Chain: AI response
    Chain->>Memory: 3. save_context(input, output)
    Memory->>Memory: Stores the exchange
    Chain->>User: Final response